Entry(0, 1)).isEqualTo(new Fraction(2, 3));\\n        assertThat(matrix.getEntry(1, 0)).isEqualTo(new Fraction(3, 4));\\n        assertThat(matrix.getEntry(1, 1)).isEqualTo(new Fraction(4, 5));\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    @SuppressWarnings(\\\"deprecation\\\")\\n    void extractsRowsFromSparseFieldMatrix() {\\n        SparseFieldMatrix<Fraction> matrix = new SparseFieldMatrix<Fraction>(FractionField.getInstance(), 2, 3);\\n        Fraction first = new Fraction(5, 6);\\n        Fraction last = new Fraction(-7, 8);\\n        matrix.setEntry(1, 0, first);\\n        matrix.setEntry(1, 2, last);\\n\\n        Fraction[] row = matrix.getRow(1);\\n\\n        assertThat(row).containsExactly(first, Fraction.ZERO, last);\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\n[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0d76feecc711c46c0169f535eb65008191834c2e8e65e99746\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp9TXvSNpTTQUSp2lbzJypukW6eu35_oJipWMon2-SL2MZW8-hjicsyZMfR33zRezNb21ikm3Ybn8WwzdPVauphNAiRVGgajoYMjdA6h-5NeL0vv_qQBtTvdqbH569DcqFK-lrPRh_mXBz1EwB-VKmBmxvRCgwEZw7Dy5el5WFREpxYO9WqktQirOnepk2_p60PLpVb2pmcXoBuzpyAQzD9_9N2cwfbwsRQnvUhWsFrAGemUQTrPaZWQXzT-41iutfBhWKs2kYgIDdwqm-gmpZcmVLDYi7bA8kHbUreJPKMhv_6MCyzgfSVty9btpZRRjnhawO9WIbny0Jp_I67BFoYmKudTFWE5fix_ujT1n5Tsw-RG7wYnUfCnrBsaYv_l5VCz3BOxm5zLYsmI6ZAcc30Rd1CyDtIrWb9MbDgS-lrQTakAhHs6VMlhkOdeneVYSDQBP3oGyv7Uan8NvGiTAiTbiaDWvXrLe3qTTzuo0lLGMy25b7NtTLtPsX_VvmVebcdF4umAXNT5fVnrtYxVxrN2BAYhh28BxpEFfSvRLuVZyeW1gtyHUxdqUlp8ibTkZEUDjGc1l8u38nCKUzMYXJMm357oRumGGfAXhkuss19nc1A1lOtea7ZWlp0jxH1WyobDEmWYSAP8iIvMG0JclFFYn3ahT6KEOWoaDVWGo8N4G1qCIhJRtZT3I1hXzcl4GGge1_toYw_Ikh_gH3vpxKzAeAKukLRNzarO0wqgDeeupNlEe2GRVwHRkKgllxV-vCk-jgXK55wpAlUE1G5eH-3sAwWfu7COAmgiO5yqG5ACnJqmIGWs82H5FfiOdNR_e17O9fEdeEdOl-rmpBgZMR9oXTLh1_WLgu7xDeA6oZIz3D4mHtELcBvjZOPbPVPokuUES3CeRsh9kgqQuoAsZwErwcHcYG6nHA-JACgV1Cj-t_Lw3JDJemdzjV1gFByrI